         <abstract id="aspace_4dfd409f465b2370e2bd9c12bf5817ba">Collection consists of color and black and white 35 mm slides of cave paintings from Dunhuang (Gansu province, China) and works from other Central Asian sites including Khotan, Kucha, and Turfan.</abstract>
      </did>
