      <prefercite id="aspace_cite">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Dunhuang (China) and Central Asian Art and Architecture Slide Collection, Arts Library, Yale University</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection consists of color and black and white 35 mm slides of cave paintings from Dunhuang (Gansu province, China) and works from other Central Asian sites including Khotan, Kucha, and Turfan.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_arr1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged by medium. Dunhuang painting sub-arranged by cave number. Central Asian material sub-arranged by site.</p>  
      </arrangement>
